content:
The trip plan is designed to meet all specified constraints while respecting the direct flight connections. Stuttgart is fixed on days 7-13 to include the conferences on day 7 and day 13. Bucharest must include a day between day 1 and day 6 for the wedding, and it is scheduled for days 1-4 to partially meet the desired 6-day visit. Warsaw is scheduled for 2 days (days 5-6) to meet the desired duration. Copenhagen and Dubrovnik are scheduled after Stuttgart, with Copenhagen for 3 days (days 14-16) to meet the desired duration, and Dubrovnik for 3 days (days 17-19), which is less than the desired 5 days but necessary due to the total day constraint. The direct flight connections are satisfied: Bucharest to Warsaw, Warsaw to Stuttgart, Stuttgart to Copenhagen, and Copenhagen to Dubrovnik.

The itinerary in the required JSON format is as follows:

```json
{
  "itinerary": [
    {
      "day_range": "Day 1-4",
      "place": "Bucharest"
    },
    {
      "day_range": "Day 5-6",
      "place": "Warsaw"
    },
    {
      "day_range": "Day 7-13",
      "place": "Stuttgart"
    },
    {
      "day_range": "Day 14-16",
      "place": "Copenhagen"
    },
    {
      "day_range": "Day 17-19",
      "place": "Dubrovnik"
    }
  ]
}
```
